### =========================================
### Better Auth Endpoints
### =========================================

# Local: Check Session (Should return null/401 unauthenticated)
GET {{baseUrlLocal}}/api/auth/get-session
Accept: application/json

###

# Remote: Check Session (Should return null/401 unauthenticated)
GET {{baseUrlRemote}}/api/auth/get-session
Accept: application/json

###

# Note: Social login endpoints like /api/auth/sign-in/social 
# are typically intended to be initiated via browser redirects natively
# rather than through REST clients.
